sentences: A passionate music fan, Latterman put together a compilation CD of his favorite unsigned bands in 1993.
He released it on his own label, and quit his job as a CPA on the day it came out.
In 2012, after more than 25 million records were sold on Aware, Latterman decided to return to school.

In 2014 he began teaching at Northwestern, where his classes examine work ethics, talent, and entrepreneurial drive, and encourage students to integrate their passions and values into their professions.
Latterman was also interested in business, and read magazines such as Forbes and Business Week as a teenager.
